{
  "_doc": "BLD.2 functional room typing. Maps a building's FUNCTION (building_types.function_of_kind) — or its raw kind — to an ORDERED list of room_types (data/room_templates.json). The FIRST room is the public/main room (assigned to the leaf that touches the entrance); the rest fill the remaining leaves by descending area. A set with <2 rooms means the building stays one open room. Ported from autonomous_world game/systems/interiors.py BUILDING_ROOM_SETS.",
